Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.10,Lyrics,,60,0,0,,{\be40}對著她就是一記飛踢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:07.06,Lyrics,,60,0,0,,{\be40}決めるまでは帰れません！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:07.06,Lyrics,,60,0,0,,{\be40}因為不成功我就回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.45,Lyrics,,0,60,0,,{\an9\be40}嫌ぁ~！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.45,Lyrics,,0,60,0,,{\an9\be40}不~！
